                <!-- 删除短评 -->
            </span>
            <span class="comment-info">
                <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Uvo/" class="">私享史</a>
                    <span>看过</span>
                    <span class="allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                <span class="comment-time " title="2012-02-09 15:10:27">
                    2012-02-09 15:10:27
                </span>
                <span class="comment-location"></span>
            </span>
        </h3>
        <p class=" comment-content">
            
                <span class="short">本片借鉴的是汉代的绘画手法，完全摒弃了西画东渐后才有的透视法，再加上用剪纸模仿皮影的特征，画面完全失去景深，别有一番味道。可惜这样的动画已经没人再做了。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="comment-report" data-url="https://movie.douban.com/subject/1431946/?comment_id=493610002"></div>
    </div>
